title: FIGHT FOR YOUR LIFE
itunes:title: FIGHT FOR YOUR LIFE
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
FIGHT FOR YOUR LIFE! Fight for your future. Fight for your family. Fight for your life, because life is a series of fights. One of the Best Speeches Ever featuring hall of fame Motivational Speaker Walter Bond (https://bit.ly/WalterBondMotiversity) and U.S. Navy Lt. Tony Ingram (https://bit.ly/TonyIngramMotiversity). Music by Epic Motiversity Music (https://bit.ly/EpicMotiversityMusic).

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
